{
  "stem": "1975.4",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Schwartz, ?] which I never knew his first name-- whom we turned over a lot of documents from the Reich Chancellery.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I want to mention to you that we have seen the corpses, the burned corpses of Eva Braun and of, of Adolf Hitler, which, for-- amazingly, the Russian command took it away.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And, and they were there, laying, for, for a few days.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But then they cleaned it up.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And for some reason, they didn't want divulge anything.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Amazingly, also, that a bomb penetrated the Reich Chancellery, a, a, a-- it's possibly American bomb or a-- or a Russian bomb, and didn't explode, and penetrated.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And during the time that I was there, I was also in charge there in turning over certain documents, which-- the Americans used to come with Studebakers.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And we used to help them load the-- all the information.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Because the Russians were not investigation.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "We, we used to investigate only certain, certain, certain parts.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But most of the paperwork, we really didn't have time for that because there was quite a lot to do in, in, in this-- in, in the sector of Berlin.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Also, we have liberated-- which, actually, I myself came in maybe-- I'd been six or seven hours afterward the concentration camp of Sachsenhausen.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And not only this, we had-- we had under our watch-- we took prisoners, the head of the-- the, the head of the camp, who was a captain.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And we took about 16 prisoners, whom we brought in for justice.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And we were going to have a, a trial, a process, parallel almost like the Nuremberg process.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And, and this was in a specific place, which is in, in a section-- in a Berlin section, which was the sector of the-- of the Russian sector.",
      "word_count": 28
    }
  ],
